            "text": "This was a game I played online against a strong anonymous 2700.\n\nA few moves ago I traded my knight for White's dark-squared bishop and advanced my g-pawn in order to try to open the position for my own bishop.\n\nLet's see how I attempted to use this piece imbalance to win the endgame.",
